BalisesLib is a set of java classes to access online weather stations data.

Today the data providers are :

- FFVL (Federation francaise de vol livre, the french free flight federation)
  http://www.ffvl.fr
  http://www.balisemeteo.com

- ROMMA
  http://www.romma.fr
 